# .projects — Maps project directory paths to project slugs
# One mapping per line: /path/to/project = project-slug
# Lines starting with # are comments. Tilde (~) is expanded.
# Omit the = project-slug part to load client context only (no project context).
#
# Examples:
#   ~/projects/client-website = website
#   ~/projects/client-app = mobile-app
#   /var/www/client = website
